### Development Guidelines

- Use Eloquent relationships, not raw queries
- Implement proper MVC separation
- Use Laravel validation
- Follow Laravel conventions
- Ensure foreign key constraints are properly set in migrations
- Use `withTimestamps()` in relationships to track enrollment dates
